{
  "doc_id": "21056",
  "text": "Hence, the matrix for an inhomogeneous system is actually quite similar to the nearly Hermitian matrix for a homogeneous system. Because QMR reduces to GMRES for Hermitian matrices in exact arithmetic [CITATION_1] , it is reasonable that the convergence behavior of QMR for an inhomogeneous system is similar to that of GMRES for a homogeneous system.",
